---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const lastUpdated = "May 14, 2026";
---
<Layout
  title="Terms &amp; Conditions | Golf Cart Rentals The Villages"
  description="Terms and conditions for Golf Cart Rentals The Villages - rental policies, driver requirements, liability, and cancellation policy."
>
  <section class="bg-slate-50 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-brand-600 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        These Terms and Conditions govern your rental of golf carts from Golf Cart Rentals The Villages (&ldquo;Company,&rdquo; &ldquo;we,&rdquo; or &ldquo;us&rdquo;). By reserving or accepting delivery of a cart, you agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">1. Driver Requirements</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>All drivers must be at least 18 years of age and hold a valid driver&rsquo;s license.</li>
        <li>The cart must only be operated within The Villages, FL and adjacent permitted cart paths and roadways.</li>
        <li>Operating the cart while impaired by alcohol or drugs is strictly prohibited and is grounds for immediate termination of the rental.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">2. Rental Periods</h2>
      <p>
        We offer weekly and monthly rentals only. Daily rentals are not available. The rental period begins on the delivery date and ends on the agreed pickup date. Early returns do not qualify for partial refunds.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">3. Reservations &amp; Payment</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>A deposit may be required at the time of booking to secure your reservation.</li>
        <li>Full balance is due before or upon delivery.</li>
        <li>Accepted payment methods: major credit cards, cash, or check (subject to clearance).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">4. Cancellation Policy</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Cancellations made more than 7 days before delivery receive a full refund of any deposit.</li>
        <li>Cancellations made within 7 days of delivery may forfeit the deposit at our discretion.</li>
        <li>No-shows and same-day cancellations are non-refundable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">5. Damage &amp; Liability</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>The cart is inspected before delivery. Any pre-existing damage will be documented.</li>
        <li>The renter is responsible for damage caused by misuse, negligence, theft, or unauthorized drivers during the rental period.</li>
        <li>Comprehensive insurance is included with every rental; specific coverage details and deductible amounts are provided in the rental agreement at delivery.</li>
        <li>The Company is not liable for personal injury, loss, or theft of personal belongings left in the cart.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">6. Maintenance &amp; Breakdowns</h2>
      <p>
        Routine maintenance is included. If you experience a mechanical issue during your rental, call us at <a href="tel:+13523064409" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">(352) 306-4409</a> between 7 AM and 7 PM and we will repair or swap the cart at no charge. Damage caused by negligence or misuse is billed to the renter.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">7. Prohibited Uses</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Off-road or beach use.</li>
        <li>Towing other vehicles or trailers.</li>
        <li>Exceeding the rated passenger capacity.</li>
        <li>Subletting or transferring the rental to another party.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">8. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of Sumter County, Florida.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">9. Force Majeure</h2>
      <p>
        We are not liable for delays or failure to perform caused by events outside our reasonable control, including weather events, hurricanes, government orders, utility outages, supply chain disruptions, or acts of God. If a Force Majeure event prevents delivery or use of the cart, we will work with you to reschedule or refund unused rental days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms and Conditions from time to time. The current version is always posted at this URL with a &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">11. SMS Terms of Service</h2>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">Golf Cart Rental SMS Program</h3>
      <p>
        By providing your phone number and checking the SMS consent box on any form on this site, you agree to receive text messages (SMS) from Golf Cart Rentals The Villages FL regarding your rental - including booking confirmations, delivery scheduling, pickup reminders, payment notifications, customer service responses, and occasional follow-up messages about your experience. Message frequency varies based on your rental activity.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">Opt-Out Instructions</h3>
      <p>
        You can opt out of our SMS program at any time. Reply <strong>STOP</strong> to any text message from us to unsubscribe. You will receive a single confirmation message and will not receive further texts from us unless you opt back in. To re-subscribe, reply <strong>START</strong> or sign up again through our website.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">Help Instructions</h3>
      <p>
        For help with our SMS program, reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message we send you, or call us at <a href="tel:+13523064409" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">(352) 306-4409</a> or email <a href="mailto:villages@mastersgolfcars.com" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">villages@mastersgolfcars.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">Message and Data Rates</h3>
      <p>
        Message and data rates may apply to any text message you receive from or send to us. Check your wireless plan for details. We are not responsible for any carrier charges you incur.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">Carrier Liability Disclaimer</h3>
      <p>
        Mobile carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages. We make no guarantee about delivery timing for any SMS message, and message delivery depends on factors outside our control, including your carrier&rsquo;s network and your device.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-6 mb-3">SMS Privacy</h3>
      <p>
        We do not sell, share, or rent your mobile phone number to any third party for marketing or promotional purposes. Phone numbers collected for our SMS program are used solely to communicate with you about your rental. See our <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">Privacy Policy</a> for full details on how we handle your personal information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">12. Compliance with Industry Standards</h2>
      <p>
        Our SMS program complies with CTIA (Cellular Telecommunications Industry Association) Messaging Principles and Best Practices and the Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA). We also comply with Twilio&rsquo;s A2P 10DLC requirements for business messaging in the United States.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-2xl text-slate-900 uppercase mt-10 mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms? Reach us at <a href="mailto:villages@mastersgolfcars.com" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">villages@mastersgolfcars.com</a> or <a href="tel:+13523064409" class="text-brand-600 font-bold">(352) 306-4409</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
